    "causal_summary": "This phase-parent decomposes that ADAPT into four independently executable children. The semantic stage runs only when lexical is empty/weak, reuses the active embedding profile's cache (default Ollama nomic-embed-text-v1.5, 768d; never embeds in the hot path), source-tags its hits, and activates them at reduced attention (`min(0.85, score)`). It ships default-off behind `SPECKIT_SEMANTIC_TRIGGERS`, shadow-first, and is promoted to union by operator policy (env-driven mode; the evidence bar is documented, not code-enforced).",
